    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从零开始建造你的家, 放置并调整墙体，选择外墙材质，加上窗户和大门。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计完美屋顶，调整天花板，装饰花园，摆放家具，甚至还能搭建阳台或门廊，一切由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/accd79f281b5743fbd790cf82e210b9b.avif?t=1754424098\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供可选的网格对齐和吸附功能，既能让你自由发挥，又能保证摆放精准整齐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 3000+ 物件和材质可供选择，随心打造最符合你风格的专属空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/ac2bcb459002b4975ac097bdb1d90783.poster.avif?t=1754424098\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/ac2bcb459002b4975ac097bdb1d90783.webm?t=1754424098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/ac2bcb459002b4975ac097bdb1d90783.mp4?t=1754424098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >细节控必备！从室内到室外，每一个角落都能按照你的喜好微调，让家充满你的个人特色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/a397944f3ae773d4ddfb2ec2d18435da.poster.avif?t=1754424098\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/a397944f3ae773d4ddfb2ec2d18435da.webm?t=1754424098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/a397944f3ae773d4ddfb2ec2d18435da.mp4?t=1754424098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切换第一人称模式，亲自步入你的梦幻之家，感受沉浸式体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/69bcac61ce196498a3382959b5168b3d.poster.avif?t=1754424098\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/69bcac61ce196498a3382959b5168b3d.webm?t=1754424098\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/69bcac61ce196498a3382959b5168b3d.mp4?t=1754424098\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用摄影模式捕捉最佳角度，分享你的作品，向世界展示你的设计才华！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014340/extras/498d2177a0e107af4fef0f02f3b728ac.avif?t=1754424098\" width=616 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦想家园设计师》(Dream Home Designer)支持动态光追、高精度贴图和精细建模，为你带来超真实的视觉享受。</p>",
